What are other ways your detail view controller could get its information? Why use segues?\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\qr\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf0 >> The detail view controller could get information by the developer manually entering in information that should be displayed on the next view controller, but this is dangerous because it allows us to pass forward information  while giving enough time to load the information. If you edit another view controller\'92s fields directly, it won\'92t have enough time and will crash. Sending information is much safer than editing views.
